title: Wok to Wok
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Choose your vegetable toppings plus a sauce, and brown or jasmine rice, and have everything stir-fried. Vegans ask to omit egg. Or choose a stir-fry or salad that's already on the menu. Food is served in an American style take away box with chopsticks or plastic cutlery. Also a location at 304 Sauchiehall Street, Glasgow.
